In the INTEREST OF L.M., D.M., and M.M., Minor Children, J.E., Mother of L.M. and D.M., Appellant, J.M., Father, Appellant. No. 19-0165 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 3, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother appeals the termination of her parental rights to two children; a father appeals the termination of his rights to three children. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
